item.title: Dharan Trip
item.description: How it all began: It was the day our one friend got to see the beauty of God’s creation in some random girl. He was so amazed by the beautiness, he couldn’t get himself out that thought. One of our friend was so going through very tough situation of life. He was sad, depressed and miserable. The whole class was worried because all those fun were lost. He of course, required some travelling .
